For rent immediately 3-room apartment with an underground parking space, at safe, monitored housing estate at Sowińskiego Street in the Wola district.
Apartment characteristics:
* 54 sq.m.;
* 3rd floor in a 6-story building;
* living room connected to the kitchen, two bedrooms, bathroom, hall, spacious balony;
* furnished - a sofa with a bedding container, a table and 2 chests of drawers in the living room, beds and wardrobes in the bedrooms and a desk in one of them, a spacious built-in wardrobe in the hall;
* equipped with household appliances - induction hob, oven, dishwasher, hood, fridge with freezer, washing machine;
* convenient parking space in the underground garage;
* large bicycle shelter, stroller room, playground in the estate, fenced estate area with 24-hour security;
* surrounded by well-kept and tidy greenery.
Location:
* located in a well-connected part of Wola, just a few minutes by car or public transport to the Księcia Janusza metro station;
* 3 parks nearby (Sowińskiego, Szymańskiego, Powstańców Warszawy) with running and cycling routes, an open gym and playing field;
* there are many service points, shops, cafes and restaurants around the estate, numerous educational institutions nearby.
Cost:
* the monthly cost is PLN 4 000, a parking space, advance payments for utilities and an administration fee included;
* guarantee deposit required;
* no commission from the tenant.
The preferred rental period is at least 1 year. Occasional rental agreement required.
Real estate agency offer. This announcement is for information purposes only and does not constitute an offer within the meaning of the Civil Code.

