The apartment consists of 4 rooms (living room with kitchenette, bedroom, office, children's room), 2 bathrooms, 2 balconies. The apartment is fully furnished, all rooms have air conditioning. The kitchen has a dishwasher, oven and induction hob, fridge, microwave - built-in equipment. The living room opens onto a large balcony. In the living room there is a sofa, shelves for books and trinkets. There is an electrically extendable projector screen hanging on the ceiling, with space for a projector opposite. There are sockets for connecting speakers in the living room and bedroom, and in the larger bathroom there are 2 speakers installed in the suspended ceiling. Both bathrooms have a toilet, one has a shower, the other has a bathtub, a washing machine and a dryer.
The bedroom has a bed and a built-in wardrobe; the bedroom has its own balcony overlooking the courtyard. The second room was a children's room - the tenant can remove the furniture. The office room can also be a room for a teenager - it is furnished with a wardrobe, a built-in desk and a sofa.
The apartment is located in a gated community with very attentive 24-hour security; in the yard there is a playground for children, two exercise equipment, lots of greenery. The apartment includes a parking space in the underground parking lot (included in the rental price).
Pets are accepted regardless of species. There were two cats in the apartment - there is a small door for cats in the door to the bedroom and one of the bathrooms, and there is room for a litter box under the cabinet. Large balcony secured with a net.
The rental price includes equipment and furnishings visible in the photos, except for the projector, speakers, computer and peripherals, books and a cat.
The apartment is located at ul. Karolkowa from the side of Szare Szeregi and Kolejowa - 500 m from Rondo Daszyńskiego, next to the 19th District.
